********** test properties **********

- only -> only  will run inside its block
 ex: describe.only only run among other describe in the block
 it.only - only run test under all describe block
 test.only - only run test under all describe block 

- skip - skip the test, syntax same as only
 
- todo - if implementation is still not done and you want to define structur of the test sui, you can define todo 

-  concurrent


*********** Alias ***********

it and test are alias and both are exactly same 
xit - alis for it.skip - it will skip it
fit - alias for it.only - only run among other test available in block 


*********** Watch mode ***********

script: {
    test: "jest --watch"
}


npm run test => It will run test as soon as we make changes and save the test file